title: C. Vivian Stringer, Celebrated Basketball Coach, Is Retiring
description: Stringer, who reached four Final Fours, won more than 1,000 games over a half-century at Cheyney State, Iowa and, finally, Rutgers.
dc:creator: Alan Blinder
category: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
media:credit: Aaron Houston for The New York Times
media:description: C. Vivian Stringer celebrating her 800th coaching win in 2008. She will finish her career with 1,055 victories.
